    "gp_section_559588505756435576": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "8938ea5dc90a862df9457bfa009242f41327b368b222b76d5514a9f687f5c3b7_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggA8eGoMQXA_text": "<p>When you place the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow between your legs, <strong>it helps keep your hips and your spine in a neutral, straight alignment.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The comfortably firm memory foam is designed to fit perfectly between your legs, giving you the ideal amount of support,preventing twisting and pulling.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This support gently stabilizes your lower body and spine, which <strong>reduces pressure on your joints, muscles, and nerves.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Normally, you would need to spend hours a week exercising to correct the misalignment, but with the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow, it happens effortlessly while you sleep.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>As your body stays supported throughout the night, <strong>you will experience pain-free sleep, wake up feeling more refreshed, and move significantly easier during daily life.</strong></p>",
        "ggKK5_keTdl_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/612b7c6ccce2485888ad0a7334313cce.mp4",
        "ggKK5_keTdl_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggKK5_keTdl_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggRHvYz4lwz_text": "<p>Did you know that misalignment of the spine during sleep can lead to pinched nerves, stiff painful joints, and restless nights?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Lack of proper lower body support while side sleeping pulls your hips and spine out of the natural alignment,</strong> which puts pressure on your joints and muscles, and reduces space around your nerves.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>As the space narrows, <strong>spinal discs start to press against the sciatic nerve</strong>, leading to compression and irritation. <strong>When this nerve gets compressed, you experience agonizing, searing pain</strong> that travels the entire length of the nerve, also known as Sciatica.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Now imagine that every single night when we sleep unsupported for hours...</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The <strong>negative impact of misalignment and pressure gets worse as we grow older,</strong> because the protective cushioning between the spinal discs and joints thins out.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This is the root cause of hip and back pain for side sleepers and the leading reason why most struggle with Sciatica.</p>",
        "ggY1FOBTJPT_text": "If You Want to Relieve Hip and Lower Back Pain… It Starts With How You Sleep",
        "ggk3P9DD54t_text": "The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow Aligns Your Spine And Releases Pressure on the Nerves And Joints",
        "ggqTbuULINK_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/612b7c6ccce2485888ad0a7334313cce.mp4",
        "ggqTbuULINK_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggqTbuULINK_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggyYdmZNRiY_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/b713d74658714c5e8ed09044c63f273a.mp4",
        "ggyYdmZNRiY_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggyYdmZNRiY_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-559588505756435576"
    },
