        "ggLW093RZa7_text": "<p>Tried, Tested, and Endorsed: Physical therapists, chiropractors, and physiotherapists recommend <strong>the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow</strong> to their clients.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And <strong>the feedback has been incredible!</strong> Many reported significantly less joint and muscle pain, meaning healthier hips, back, and legs. The result? Better sleep, reduced stress, and no pain.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>What sets the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow apart? The innovative design, unique premium materials, and soft elastic strap that keeps the pillow in place even as you toss and turn.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For <strong>a fraction of what you would spend on conventional therapy,</strong> the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow offers long-lasting relief, and a professional level of care.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s a one-time affordable investment in your (sleep) health that you simply cannot ignore.</p>",
        "ggRrP-62Kic_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow has become a <strong>nationwide favorite!</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Countless people reported massive improvements after just a few nights with the pillow! And almost everyone continues using it every night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Within a few nights of using the <strong>SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow,</strong> you can expect to start noticing reduced discomfort and better sleep.</p>",
        "ggTJiycYfKs_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/42f87d03787b45d888c6df8d4109c5d9.mp4",
        "ggTJiycYfKs_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggTJiycYfKs_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg_-pF50g9y_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/1d566132d8a94c4891ac85a5702f66e7.mp4",
        "gg_-pF50g9y_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg_-pF50g9y_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggfj4F0mUQq_text": "Professionally Designed &amp; Recommended",
        "gglZ0gcwAvm_text": "<p><strong>No more waking up with painful hips or a sore back.</strong></p>",
        "ggmqBzP3i-R_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-97042735-715a-4957-901b-946ce11e026d.svg",
        "ggnbFRB_HFB_text": "<p>Order your SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow today… Use it for up to 3 full months… And then <strong>decide based on the results if you want to keep it or not anytime during the 90-night period.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you’re not happy with the results, feel like it hasn’t improved your sleep, or did not help relieve pain, we’ll give you a full refund – no questions asked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So it either <strong>helps you sleep better and relieve pain in your hips, back and legs like advertised,</strong> or you get your money back the same day.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That’s how confident we are in the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow.</p>",
        "ggoskO8o_bu_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-97042735-715a-4957-901b-946ce11e026d.svg",
        "ggrVkrkcFqn_text": "<p><strong>No more discomfort that keeps you from enjoying your life.</strong></p>",
        "ggxP0uka1UT_text": "<p>Just place the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow between your legs, get comfortable, and enjoy all the benefits of a normal life.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Plus, the elastic strap is uniquely designed to fit all leg sizes no matter your thigh circumference</p>",
        "ggzZ-A2Csf9_text": "Don’t Just Take Our Word for It… Try It for 90 Nights Risk-Free"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-559588505756501112"
