    "gp_section_559588505756828792": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "b77ecbb3cf71a3bc7590710cabb554b07977bb87575e10a56c173eaab684fcc8_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg0jtXNKmgS_text": "John M.",
        "gg3hA8Ly82r_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-2792ff6e-63ea-440d-a210-3e3beab4c977.jpg",
        "gg88tlhYBI0_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-9469a84d-2fad-4ab6-b7a0-e94ca3e63283.jpg",
        "gg9HIZthPVv_text": "<p>I love that it stays in place, because I move a lot during the night, but this pillow doesn't wake me up at all. I tried a couple other pillows before, even put a bunch of different memory foam head pillows between my legs, but nothing comes close. I get out of bed a lot easier and going up the stairs doesn't hurt anymore. My husband also loves that I don't wake up 10 times a night anymore, which helps us both sleep better.</p>",
        "ggJD-XsBBvl_text": "<p>I've been struggling with hip pain, sciatica, arthritis, and spinal stenosis for years, and nothing seemed to help. I decided to give the smoothspine pillow a try, and I am amazed at the difference it has made. For the first time in years, I wake up without pain. The support it gives keeps my spine and hips in what feels like the perfect position, which helps me to sleep a lot better. I highly recommend this pillow to anyone suffering from similar issues.</p>",
        "ggL9Uwy4srb_text": "Emily T.",
        "ggOZsOehFV2_text": "Everyone Loves the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow!",
        "ggRp8NMORoz_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-35b675f5-8071-44da-a7ef-2dedb9f8de24.jpg",
        "ggoxI5hysa-_text": "<p>Skeptical! Yes, that was me before ordering this. As a side sleeper, I've had issues with back and hip pain for the longest time. I didn't believe a pillow like this from smoothspine could change it, as I assumed it would require consistent treatments. I already spent a small fortune on those, so I decided I had nothing to lose trying this. This is hands down the best investment I've made for my pain, I wish I found it sooner.</p>",
        "ggxLIAZvbhG_text": "Jennifer C."
      },
      "type": "gp-section-559588505756828792"
    },
    "gp_section_559588505756894328": {
