      "settings": {
        "checksum": "b2cb326de6b2d32e2f2754b5b10e16a0eb6d835442b0c6076d3981defbda68cc_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg8-Mcm0GP7_childItem_0": "<p>What is your return policy?</p>",
        "gg94eJ_UnWu_text": "<p>Upon placing your order you will receive a full guide in your inbox on different ways and recommendations for the use of the pillow such as positioning. Anyone, no matter age, gender or condition can use it. Simple as that!</p><p>We also have a few videos on our Facebook page demonstrating putting the pillow on and using it.</p>",
        "ggDIwQjBcZJ_text": "<p>Yes! Not only will it prevent spine misalignment, but it will also prevent bone-on-bone rubbing, meaning pain-free and comfortable side sleeping.</p>",
        "ggIKj7dCe0R_childItem_0": "<p>Shipping FAQ</p>",
        "ggL_8FrrvK9_text": "<p>If you've ever felt like pain or discomfort in your back, hips or knees kept you from the a night of uninterrupted sleep - then the relief and comfort our pillow provides can significantly improve your sleep, yes!</p>",
        "ggPgOk3MO7z_text": "<p>✔ All credit cards (Including VISA, Mastercard, Maestro, American Express)<br>✔ Apple Pay and Google Pay<br>✔ Shopify Pay</p>",
        "ggQsNASS0gZ_childItem_0": "<p>Does it improve my sleep?</p>",
        "ggRPWjH9Naz_text": "<p>The <strong>90-Night Money-Back Guarantee</strong> is our way of ensuring your complete satisfaction with our products. If you are not satisfied with the result, then let us know within 90 nights after receiving your order, and we will give you a full refund. We might request additional information from the customer in case the product is reported as defective or faulty. The cost of shipping for returned items is covered by customers.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We do not refund refused packages or returned to the address not confirmed by us. If you have an issue with your order or product please email support@smoothspine.com.</p>",
        "ggSr6jCa52i_childItem_0": "<p>What payment methods do you accept?</p>",
        "ggalKqcOp4A_childItem_0": "<p>Will this pillow help with my back, hip or knee pain?</p>",
        "ggqDO0N33NY_text": "<p>85%* of our customers report significant improvements in their sleep, back, hips and knees after the very first night of sleeping with the SmoothSpine Leg Pillow.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Please do not worry if this is not you! Everyone's body is different, so some people need a couple trial nights before getting used to sleeping with our pillow and to be able to feel the relief. This is exactly why our policy lasts 90 nights - to guarantee results, even if you need a couple nights to get used to your improved way of sleeping.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>*Results according to a survey done by 412 customers.</p>",
        "ggu75t3hm_a_text": "<p><strong>We are proud to offer Tracked Shipping on all orders Worldwide</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Free shipping on all orders over $60.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>To ensure a safe and smooth delivery process, the standard shipping &amp; handling price for orders below the free shipping threshold is $3.95-$4.95 (depending on the type of products and amount of products ordered).</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Priority shipping prices vary for each country (specified during checkout).</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Standard Shipping Times* </strong>(in business days):</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>USA: 7 - 12 days (delivered by USPS or FedEx)</strong><br><strong>United Kingdom: 6 - 8 days</strong><br><strong>Canada: 12 days&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Asia: 12 days&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Europe: 10 - 12 days&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Australia: 10 - 12 days</strong><br><strong>New Zealand: 10 - 12 days</strong><br><strong>Other countries: ~12 days</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We aim to dispatch all orders from our warehouse within 48 hours, but please allow up to 5 business days during peak periods.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When your items are shipped out, you should receive a notification from us via email providing you with a tracking number.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you haven't received the email or if the tracking number doesn't work, it’s okay. Contact us and we will fix it!</p><p>*Shipping time excludes clearance/customs delays (if applicable).</p>",
        "ggv0OhSvZXn_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggwHBcl2AFL_childItem_0": "<p>How fast will the pillow help me?</p>",
        "ggwlyVohdEP_text": "<p>No, our custom made memory foam ensures the SmoothSpine Leg Pillow does not get annoyingly hot. It does get a little warm which is unavoidable, however, this only helps the memory foam to do what it does best; shape to your legs!</p><p>This makes the SmoothSpine Leg Pillow the perfect fit all year round.</p>",
        "ggxLUswgNyK_childItem_0": "<p>How to use the pillow?</p>",
        "ggz8cSR5vW4_childItem_0": "<p>Does the pillow get hot?</p>"
      },
